187
00:13:53,104 --> 00:13:54,104
commander

188
00:13:54,604 --> 00:13:55,719
please proceed

189
00:14:10,896 --> 00:14:12,352
These herbs are harsh

190
00:14:13,521 --> 00:14:16,263
in an hour

191
00:14:16,271 --> 00:14:17,807
